This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses deep neural networks for video frame prediction (cs.CV) and reward prediction (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of model-based techniques (cs.RO) and the need for data efficiency (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, followed by cs.RO and cs.NE.
